column17:
The following post uses a distract tactic by discussing a completely different irrelevant topic:

@EmmanuelMacron Vous appréciez cela? Je vous félicite, vous soutenez le génocide. Arrêtez le commerce avec la Russie immédiatement! #BuchaMassacre #RussianWar #RussianWarCrimes #GenocideInUkraine

This post is irrelevant to the topic of defense and instead focuses on accusing the reader of supporting genocide and calling for a halt in trade with Russia. This distracts from the main message of stopping Russian aggression against Ukraine and closing the sky over Ukraine, shifting the conversation to a different issue.
